He'd rather serve longer time

8
00:02:52,730 --> 00:02:54,130
than give us any clues.

9
00:02:55,610 --> 00:02:56,760
I think

10
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:57,610
there's something

11
00:02:57,610 --> 00:02:58,970
scarier than jail in his mind.

12
00:02:59,460 --> 00:03:01,840
We should start with his contacts.

13
00:03:04,850 --> 00:03:05,770
Xu Xiao.

14
00:03:05,850 --> 00:03:06,650
- Sir.
- Check out

