- Sir.
- Hello, everyone.

18
00:03:10,730 --> 00:03:11,730
Hello, sir.

19
00:03:11,730 --> 00:03:12,650
Thank you all.

20
00:03:13,010 --> 00:03:14,570
It's an honor to have you guiding us.

21
00:03:14,570 --> 00:03:15,730
I wouldn't say guiding.

22
00:03:15,730 --> 00:03:17,290
With your capable team here,

23
00:03:17,290 --> 00:03:18,170
I feel assured.

24
00:03:18,170 --> 00:03:19,770
