25
00:03:19,890 --> 00:03:20,810
Right, Director Yang?

26
00:03:21,140 --> 00:03:22,580
We appreciate it.

27
00:03:25,980 --> 00:03:27,820
Commissioner Cao heard
of your case's progress

28
00:03:27,820 --> 00:03:28,900
and made a visit today.

29
00:03:29,820 --> 00:03:31,540
Yes, there has been progress,

30
00:03:31,540 --> 00:03:32,620
but at the same time,

31
00:03:32,940 --> 00:03:34,180
new challenges have emerged.

32
00:03:34,980 --> 00:03:36,940
There's a suspect

33
00:03:36,940 --> 00:03:37,820
who might hold info

34
00:03:37,820 --> 00:03:39,500
(Suspect Zhou Daming)
crucial to the case,

35
00:03:39,500 --> 00:03:40,580
yet he's not cooperating.

36
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:42,620
So we're meeting to discuss strategies.

37
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:45,170
Xiaoxing, give an introduction.

38
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:47,740
Laosan's

39
00:03:47,740 --> 00:03:49,420
real name is Shen Chao. A core member

40
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:51,540
of Zhou Daming's grave-robbing gang.

41
00:03:51,780 --> 00:03:53,300
His main role was to handle

42
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:55,220
explosives for tomb entry.

43
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:56,860
He likely learned this skill

44
00:03:56,860 --> 00:03:59,380
from his early mining work.

45
00:03:59,740 --> 00:04:01,340
We're still tracking

46
00:04:01,340 --> 00:04:02,380
the explosive's origin.

47
00:04:03,620 --> 00:04:04,700
We noticed

48
00:04:04,900 --> 00:04:05,740
Shen Chao

49
00:04:05,740 --> 00:04:06,680
is addicted to gambling,

50
00:04:06,740 --> 00:04:07,740
but strangely,

51
00:04:07,740 --> 00:04:08,860
he has no gambling debts.

52
00:04:08,860 --> 00:04:10,460
We suspect

53
00:04:10,460 --> 00:04:11,820
he bets in small amounts.

54
00:04:12,140 --> 00:04:13,380
According to call records,

55
00:04:14,180 --> 00:04:16,140
besides Zhou and other gamblers,

56
00:04:16,460 --> 00:04:17,540
the person he contacts most

57
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:19,060
is Du Lanlan.

58
00:04:19,460 --> 00:04:20,620
This is her.

59
00:04:20,620 --> 00:04:21,540
32 years old,

60
00:04:21,540 --> 00:04:22,940
single mother of a 4-year-old,

61
00:04:22,980 --> 00:04:24,300
running a small leather shop.

62
00:04:24,540 --> 00:04:25,460
Shen Chao and Du Lanlan

63
00:04:25,460 --> 00:04:26,810
must have an unusual relationship.

64
00:04:26,980 --> 00:04:28,100
Over the past few years,

65
00:04:28,100 --> 00:04:30,180
there were frequent transfers between them.

66
00:04:30,980 --> 00:04:32,420
The biggest was two years ago.

67
00:04:32,420 --> 00:04:34,620
Shen Chao transferred her
500,000 yuan in one go.

68
00:04:35,060 --> 00:04:36,940
She later opened her leather store.

69
00:04:38,540 --> 00:04:39,860
Could Du Lanlan be the key

70
00:04:39,860 --> 00:04:41,500
to cracking this case?

71
00:04:41,860 --> 00:04:42,780
We hope so.

72
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:44,940
I'm planning to visit her tomorrow.

73
00:04:45,220 --> 00:04:46,140
I'll come with you.

74
00:04:46,620 --> 00:04:47,540
No need, Lin.

75
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:48,460
I've got this.

76
00:05:30,420 --> 00:05:32,060
Shen Chao's unwilling to talk.

77
00:05:32,980 --> 00:05:34,030
Looks like he's trying

78
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,480
to take the fall himself.

79
00:05:36,220 --> 00:05:37,540
Let me be clear.

80
00:05:37,540 --> 00:05:38,460
This could get him

81
00:05:38,980 --> 00:05:39,900
in serious trouble.

82
00:05:47,540 --> 00:05:48,860
He's not from Zhouli Village.

83
00:05:50,180 --> 00:05:52,420
No need to go down with those

84
00:05:52,420 --> 00:05:53,580
tomb raiders.

85
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:55,420
If he confesses,

86
00:05:56,180 --> 00:05:57,380
he might get

87
00:05:57,860 --> 00:05:58,780
a reduced sentence

88
00:05:58,940 --> 00:05:59,940
and get out sooner.

89
00:06:03,350 --> 00:06:04,560
We're not married.

90
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:06,720
What happens to him

91
00:06:07,490 --> 00:06:08,420
is not my concern.

92
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:18,740
It took the plate away.

93
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:26,160
Is that your son?

94
00:06:29,860 --> 00:06:30,820
What a pretty boy.

95
00:06:42,780 --> 00:06:43,700
Nice kid.

96
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:46,620
A bright future is

97
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:47,620
waiting for him.

98
00:06:49,060 --> 00:06:50,060
Imagine him

99
00:06:50,420 --> 00:06:51,740
graduating college,

100
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:54,180
wearing his cap and gown.

101
00:06:54,980 --> 00:06:55,980
You'll get

102
00:06:55,980 --> 00:06:57,180
a family photo

103
00:06:57,980 --> 00:06:59,300
on campus.

104
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:03,940
A brand-new life begins.

105
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:05,780
How wonderful.

106
00:07:17,300 --> 00:07:18,380
Can I visit him?

107
00:07:35,300 --> 00:07:36,220
Number three.

108
00:07:36,980 --> 00:07:37,900
Go ahead.

109
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:14,940
Dad, why are you in there?

110
00:08:15,540 --> 00:08:17,620
When are you coming home?

111
00:08:17,780 --> 00:08:19,740
I miss you.

112
00:08:20,540 --> 00:08:21,620
Good boy.

113
00:08:22,660 --> 00:08:24,060
I'll be home soon.

114
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:27,860
Dad, your yellow vest looks funny.

115
00:08:36,140 --> 00:08:37,220
Take him back.

116
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:03,380
(Interrogation Room)
Captain Xu.

117
00:09:03,420 --> 00:09:04,620
That guy's a tough nut.

118
00:09:05,060 --> 00:09:05,980
Will this tactic work?

119
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:08,380
Worth a try, right?

120
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:12,820
Captain Xu.

121
00:09:20,420 --> 00:09:21,340
They visited?

122
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:22,820
Yes.

123
00:09:25,420 --> 00:09:26,340
You must

124
00:09:26,890 --> 00:09:27,980
guarantee

125
00:09:28,180 --> 00:09:30,620
my family's safety.

126
00:09:34,420 --> 00:09:35,740
I can guarantee that.

127
00:09:36,300 --> 00:09:37,780
Only if you cooperate.

128
00:09:38,420 --> 00:09:39,340
I will.

129
00:09:40,140 --> 00:09:42,380
I didn't set the explosives.

130
00:09:43,300 --> 00:09:45,380
I had no grudge against Zhou Daming.

131
00:09:45,860 --> 00:09:46,740
For many years,

132
00:09:46,740 --> 00:09:48,220
he's treated me well.

133
00:09:48,580 --> 00:09:50,700
I've worked at the mine for years.

134
00:09:51,140 --> 00:09:52,580
I'm careful with explosives.

135
00:09:53,380 --> 00:09:54,340
The explosive was

136
00:09:54,660 --> 00:09:56,580
definitely planted

137
00:09:56,740 --> 00:09:57,740
ahead of time.

138
00:09:58,380 --> 00:09:59,340
I don't know

139
00:10:00,260 --> 00:10:01,340
how it was triggered.

140
00:10:02,380 --> 00:10:04,140
The reason I didn't tell you

141
00:10:04,140 --> 00:10:05,060
is because

142
00:10:06,580 --> 00:10:07,940
that was too brutal.

143
00:10:09,140 --> 00:10:10,940
I'm afraid of getting involved.

144
00:10:13,260 --> 00:10:14,660
In your line of work,

145
00:10:15,660 --> 00:10:17,460
who else

146
00:10:17,660 --> 00:10:18,660
knows this skill?

147
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:19,580
Probably

148
00:10:20,380 --> 00:10:21,660
no more than five people.

149
00:10:22,860 --> 00:10:24,940
If you want their names,

150
00:10:25,780 --> 00:10:27,060
I can tell you all of them.

151
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:29,060
But they're all street names.

152
00:10:29,410 --> 00:10:30,420
I don't know

153
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:31,660
their real names.

154
00:10:32,380 --> 00:10:33,300
Did Zhou Daming

155
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:34,700
have enemies?

156
00:10:35,500 --> 00:10:36,420
Yeah.

157
00:10:36,580 --> 00:10:37,500
Quite a few.

158
00:10:37,980 --> 00:10:39,940
He gambled,

159
00:10:40,500 --> 00:10:42,220
got into fights,

160
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:43,580
sometimes

161
00:10:43,580 --> 00:10:46,060
even harassed widows

162
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:47,860
when he was drunk.

163
00:10:48,140 --> 00:10:49,700
Anyone

164
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,000
particularly strange

165
00:10:52,140 --> 00:10:53,740
in his circle?

166
00:10:54,980 --> 00:10:56,220
When you say strange,

167
00:10:56,740 --> 00:10:57,740
what do you mean?

168
00:10:57,740 --> 00:10:59,460
How strange?

169
00:11:03,380 --> 00:11:05,460
Someone who gives you a feeling,

170
00:11:08,020 --> 00:11:08,940
something's off.

171
00:11:11,140 --> 00:11:12,060
Like when you see them,

172
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:13,700
you feel they

173
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:14,780
really like

174
00:11:15,140 --> 00:11:16,140
superstitions.

175
00:11:16,140 --> 00:11:17,420
Into Feng Shui and that.

176
00:11:17,420 --> 00:11:18,340
Know anyone like that?

177
00:11:19,420 --> 00:11:20,340
Yes.

178
00:11:21,420 --> 00:11:22,380
There is one.

179
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:24,220
Who?

180
00:11:25,060 --> 00:11:26,020
That person is

181
00:11:28,060 --> 00:11:29,380
Zhou's handler.

182
00:11:29,780 --> 00:11:30,780
But

183
00:11:30,780 --> 00:11:32,260
I've never met him.

184
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:33,980
I don't know his name.

185
00:11:35,020 --> 00:11:35,900
Once,

186
00:11:35,900 --> 00:11:37,500
Zhou called him.

187
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:38,700
I felt

188
00:11:38,900 --> 00:11:40,460
Zhou was very respectful.

189
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:42,060
On the phone,

190
00:11:42,060 --> 00:11:43,660
he called him Boss.

191
00:11:44,300 --> 00:11:45,300
Another time,

192
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:46,540
I had dinner with Zhou.

193
00:11:46,540 --> 00:11:47,460
He drank too much

194
00:11:48,260 --> 00:11:49,340
and told us,

195
00:11:50,180 --> 00:11:51,420
his boss

196
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:52,380
was quite mysterious.

197
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:54,620
How?

198
00:11:55,820 --> 00:11:56,780
The Boss

199
00:11:56,940 --> 00:11:58,020
has a coffin

200
00:11:58,380 --> 00:11:59,580
in his bedroom.

201
00:12:01,300 --> 00:12:02,500
He finds it

202
00:12:02,660 --> 00:12:03,660
pretty good

203
00:12:03,660 --> 00:12:05,500
and sleeps in there every night.

204
00:12:09,700 --> 00:12:10,620
Says it

205
00:12:11,420 --> 00:12:12,620
helps his health.

206
00:12:16,700 --> 00:12:18,180
When did Zhou Daming and the Boss

207
00:12:18,180 --> 00:12:19,660
last talk?

208
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,580
Do you

209
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,580
remember?

210
00:12:21,700 --> 00:12:22,780
No idea.

211
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:24,420
But

212
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:26,900
the day we went down into the tomb,

213
00:12:26,900 --> 00:12:28,380
after our meeting,

214
00:12:29,180 --> 00:12:31,660
Zhou said he had to meet the Boss first.

215
00:12:31,660 --> 00:12:32,660
Because that tomb

216
00:12:33,820 --> 00:12:35,500
was pointed out by the Boss.

217
00:12:38,380 --> 00:12:40,140
Does the Boss know explosives?

218
00:12:40,420 --> 00:12:41,460
Zhou said

219
00:12:41,780 --> 00:12:42,700
he was an expert.

220
00:12:47,290 --> 00:12:48,190
How did he get there?

221
00:12:48,210 --> 00:12:49,300
I drove him.

222
00:12:49,780 --> 00:12:50,700
Remember the address?

223
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:52,500
1206.

224
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:54,060
Kuilin Community.

225
00:13:07,900 --> 00:13:09,380
Based on Shen Chao's confession,

226
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:11,620
we checked the surveillance from that day.

227
00:13:11,780 --> 00:13:12,660
They indeed stopped

228
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:14,500
in front of Building 1206.

229
00:13:16,180 --> 00:13:17,100
Hey, Captain.

230
00:13:17,290 --> 00:13:18,140
How did you know

231
00:13:18,140 --> 00:13:19,380
Du Lanlan could make him talk?

232
00:13:19,700 --> 00:13:21,260
She's two years older,

233
00:13:21,460 --> 00:13:22,300
divorced,

234
00:13:22,300 --> 00:13:23,160
and has a kid.

235
00:13:23,180 --> 00:13:24,300
But since early this year,

236
00:13:24,300 --> 00:13:25,560
they've been tying up the lines.

237
00:13:25,570 --> 00:13:26,500
Why?

238
00:13:27,380 --> 00:13:28,300
Mistress?

239
00:13:29,060 --> 00:13:29,980
True love.

240
00:13:31,900 --> 00:13:33,980
What's one's biggest weakness?

241
00:13:35,070 --> 00:13:35,910
The biggest…

242
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:38,140
Kids are our biggest weakness.

243
00:13:40,060 --> 00:13:41,500
What do you mean, Lin?

244
00:13:41,780 --> 00:13:43,660
You'll understand once you have one.

245
00:14:16,420 --> 00:14:17,340
This is the place.

246
00:14:17,580 --> 00:14:18,500
1206.

247
00:14:20,740 --> 00:14:22,720
It has Room 1206?

248
00:14:24,820 --> 00:14:26,380
Room 206, Building One.

249
00:14:28,420 --> 00:14:29,320
Alright.

250
00:14:29,690 --> 00:14:30,740
Find the property manager

251
00:14:31,300 --> 00:14:32,860
and get the resident info.

252
00:14:33,060 --> 00:14:33,980
Lin, let's go up.

253
00:14:39,490 --> 00:14:40,380
Uh…

254
00:14:40,380 --> 00:14:41,780
Is there a manager here?

255
00:14:41,780 --> 00:14:43,300
There must be.

256
00:14:44,060 --> 00:14:45,820
It's a proper complex.

257
00:14:45,820 --> 00:14:46,740
Look around.

258
00:15:06,060 --> 00:15:06,980
Over here.

259
00:15:59,380 --> 00:16:00,300
Lin.

260
00:16:37,180 --> 00:16:38,100
Lin.

261
00:17:11,620 --> 00:17:12,540
What's that smell?

262
00:17:15,540 --> 00:17:16,620
Seems like window caulk.

263
00:17:33,020 --> 00:17:33,940
Let me.

264
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:35,020
No need.

265
00:17:54,100 --> 00:17:55,740
(Monkfruit, Astragalus, Tai Bai Hua)

266
00:17:56,940 --> 00:17:58,340
("Ancient Prose Anthology")

267
00:18:11,380 --> 00:18:12,300
All done?

268
00:18:13,300 --> 00:18:14,220
Yeah.

269
00:18:18,580 --> 00:18:19,740
Three, two,

270
00:18:19,740 --> 00:18:20,700
one.

271
00:18:34,580 --> 00:18:36,220
We've met him, right?

272
00:18:41,260 --> 00:18:42,620
I'm Hu Xiaomin.

273
00:18:42,620 --> 00:18:43,620
(Fresh Every Day)

274
00:18:43,620 --> 00:18:44,820
(Hu Xiaomin)
I run a grocery store.

275
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:47,380
We get some frozen chicken and eggs

276
00:18:47,620 --> 00:18:49,180
from him monthly.

277
00:18:51,100 --> 00:18:52,020
Hu Xiaomin?

278
00:18:52,540 --> 00:18:53,460
That's right.

279
00:18:53,820 --> 00:18:54,820
Hu Xiaomin.

280
00:18:57,540 --> 00:18:58,780
You guys go ahead.

281
00:18:58,780 --> 00:18:59,700
I'm leaving now.

282
00:18:59,820 --> 00:19:01,140
How could it be him?

283
00:19:53,940 --> 00:19:54,860
Where was it found?

284
00:19:55,460 --> 00:19:56,580
Under Zhou Daming's pillow.

285
00:20:11,700 --> 00:20:12,620
Captain Xu,

286
00:20:12,940 --> 00:20:14,100
hit on the head from a bottle,

287
00:20:14,100 --> 00:20:14,980
but it wasn't fatal.

288
00:20:14,980 --> 00:20:16,810
He was dragged into the coffin
and suffocated.

289
00:20:16,940 --> 00:20:18,300
There's caulking glue in his mouth.

290
00:20:18,700 --> 00:20:20,020
Estimated time of death is

291
00:20:20,040 --> 00:20:20,990
two to three days ago.

292
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,360
Broken glass near the coffee table

293
00:20:22,370 --> 00:20:23,660
matches his head wound.

294
00:20:23,940 --> 00:20:25,150
It should be the primary scene.

295
00:20:25,180 --> 00:20:26,020
The coffin was sealed

296
00:20:26,020 --> 00:20:27,220
by common window caulk.

297
00:20:27,220 --> 00:20:29,140
25 yuan per tube at any market.

298
00:20:29,660 --> 00:20:30,580
Fingerprints?

299
00:20:30,860 --> 00:20:32,180
Several sets were collected.

300
00:20:32,180 --> 00:20:33,860
Both victim's and Zhou Daming's.

